  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个早晨起床后的流程图，从醒来开始，然后是洗澡、穿衣服，最后做咖啡和喝咖啡。你能帮我梳理一下吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAKE_UP",
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE",
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解了。这里有两个类别对吧？selfcare 是个人护理，food 是饮食相关。那顺序是严格的线性流程吗？洗澡一定要在穿衣服之前？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，顺序很重要，必须先洗澡再穿衣服。另外做咖啡和喝咖啡也是连续的，不能跳过。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE",
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白，我先画出来：WAKE_UP 作为起点，然后连到 SHOWER，再到 GET_DRESSED。不过这里有个问题——穿衣服之后直接连到 MAKE_COFFEE 吗？中间需要加点什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAKE_UP",
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不需要，直接连就行。这个流程比较理想化，假设衣服穿好了就去厨房做咖啡。对了，节点命名我想统一用大写，类别前缀保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已经调整：selfcare::GET_DRESSED 指向 food::MAKE_COFFEE，然后 MAKE_COFFEE 再连到 DRINK_COFFEE。这样整个链条就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE",
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，WAKE_UP 这个节点，它前面不需要类别前缀吗？它好像不属于 selfcare 也不属于 food。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAKE_UP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确实，WAKE_UP 是起始动作，可以不加前缀保持简洁。或者你觉得需要加个类似 routine:: 的前缀？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAKE_UP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用加了，WAKE_UP 单独放就好，这样视觉上起点更清晰。我确认一下整体顺序：醒来 → 洗澡 → 穿衣 → 做咖啡 → 喝咖啡，没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAKE_UP",
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE",
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，五个节点，四条连线，全部是单向顺序执行。SHOWER 和 GET_DRESSED 归在 selfcare 下，MAKE_COFFEE 和 DRINK_COFFEE 归在 food 下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "selfcare::SHOWER",
        "selfcare::GET_DRESSED",
        "food::MAKE_COFFEE",
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一个小调整——DRINK_COFFEE 作为终点，要不要考虑后面还能扩展？比如加个工作相关的分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以先留着，目前 DRINK_COFFEE 作为叶子节点，以后扩展很方便。现在的版本已经完整描述了早晨 routine，需要我最终确认一遍结构吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "food::DRINK_COFFEE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
